

Servlet : 

Servlet-->Http--->HttpServlet
Servlet-->GenericServlet

Servlet Life Cycle : 

1)init()
2)service()
3)destroy()

public/protected void init(HttpServletRequest request,
HttpServletResponse response)throws ServletException,IOException
		{
		
		}


Method Calling : 
1)
init(request,response)
{
}

2)
service(request,response)
{
doService(request,response);
}

doService(request,response)
{
doGet(request,response);
}

doGet(request,response)
{
Servlet Code
or
doPost(request,response);
}

doPost(request,response)
{
Servlet Code
}

3)
destroy(request,response)
{

}


doGet():
-url visible in address bar
-not secure
-can forward only 256kb data with request and response 

doPost():
-url not visible in address bar
-secure
-No Limit for sending  data with request and response 


http://localhost:8081/ips8/HelloServlet?t1=

http://localhost:8081/ips8/HelloServlet?t1=Kal+Test+Ho+Sakta+He+Agar+40+%2B+student+class+me+ate+he+to.+Nahi+to+Kal+Servlet+Pura+Pada+Diya+Jayega.








